  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aims of this study are:

        1. to investigate if HIV infection alters the antibody responses to influenza and

        2. to assess the ability of licensed influenza vaccine to induce functional
           non-neutralising antibodies in HIV-infected and HIV-uninfected subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
